From the github issue:
Initial desired state:
{ “a” : 1, “b” : 2 }

If customer sends PATCH { “a” : -1} device will receive { “a” : -1 }. If customer sends PATCH { “a”: 1, “b”: 2 } device will receive { “a”: 1, “b”: 2 }

Having said that, if customer sends PUT { “a” : 1, “c” : 100 }, device will get { “a”: 1, “b”: null, “c” : 100 }

